.SS Principle: security belongs in the normal loop
Why it matters:
.PP
Security work fails when it is treated as a separate phase with weak
feedback.
.PP
How it applies here:
.IP \(bu 2
scans are part of \f[CR]task ci\f[R]
.IP \(bu 2
dependency and secret findings should be inspected as normal engineering
work
.PP
Failure mode:
.IP \(bu 2
